  "body": "# Bug Report\n\n## Problem\nContinuation of https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/10274\nFrom user POV: It just jumps, as if itâ€™s refreshing the chat.\nFor example, if you scroll up a few messages and then someone sends a new message to the chat, you will notice the chat jump so you know a new message has appeared.\n\n\n#### Expected behavior\nscroll position is the same\n\n#### Actual behavior\nchat is autoscrolling on each new messages, so you can't read history if new messages are appearing fast\n![ezgif com-video-to-gif (1)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/79461701-cf033e00-7ff6-11ea-9ffd-0a18f1aa5229.gif)\n\n\n### Reproduction\n\n- Open Status\n- Join some public chat with history\n- Scroll up to read history\n- From another device send big message to this public chat\n\n### Additional Information\n\n- Status version: nightly 16/04/2020\n- Operating System: Android, iOS",
